beer.beer_description:
Swan Draught is the pick of the crop when it comes to easy drinking lagers. Smooth and full-bodied, with just the right amount of malty richness, this draught beer is refreshing and satiating all at once.

An ideal source of fresh water for making quality beer, the Swan River was identified by Frederick Sherwood in 1857, as the perfect location for Swan Brewery.

Malts: Pale Lager and Roasted Malt

Hops: Super Pride and Hop Extract

Yeast: Australian Lager Yeast

Additions: Cane Sugar
